text.__SUMMARY__: Lithocarpus neorobinsonii is a species of plant in the family Fagaceae. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia.
text.References: Chua, L.S.L. (1998). "Lithocarpus neorobinsonii". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T31503A9637440. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31503A9637440.en. Retrieved 18 December 2017.
